description:
&lt;p&gt;As part of the service expansion the Level 5 Operating Theatres situated at The Royal Sussex County Hospital is seeking a highly motivated individuals to join its team of Healthcare Assistants in order to help support the delivery of major elective and emergency surgery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Healthcare Assistant you will support the qualified Nurses and ODPs in the delivery of peri-operative patient care across of range of different surgical specialties.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Department offers its own internal training programme, so although experience is an advantage it is not necessary.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In return you can expect to work within a friendly and recently refurbished Department. The Trust has its own Training Department and you would be expected to study for a Care Sector qualification.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name Tom Osborne&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title Acting Theatre Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address osborne.tom@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
